ns-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\">\n   <div style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;letter-spacing: inherit;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px -30px;padding: 0px;hyphens: auto;letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 16px;color: transparent;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;width: 30px;height: 30px;border-radius: 50%;background: rgba(1, 169, 216, 0.3);overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">1</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px 0px 24px;margin:0px 0px 0px 15px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:20px;line-height:1.75em;hyphens:auto;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI版“小程序商店”</span></strong></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">Macaron还内置了一个“灵感库”，左上角那个很小立方体是入口，简单说，就是一个内置的应用商店。里面是官方筛选的一些小应用。开玩笑的说，微信不敢做的它做了。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quo